data.description: Peaceful living in the Lake Nahwatzel community! This adorable property offers cozy cabin-style living on 2+ ac. With 4 beds, 2 baths, and 3 floors of living space, there is enough room for everyone! Ideal for a permanent residence, 2nd summer home, or short-term rental! Wonderful work space in the 2-car garage and space for RV parking. Enjoy summer fun on the water with easy access to the lake from the public boat launch. This is your opportunity!
